              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成1点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">清净之园囿</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/2a7181cfb07c093325abc8170e210e45_4152603843820419219.png",
