                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "神里流 · 水囿"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">结束阶段：</span>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：2</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">此召唤物在场时：</span>我方角色<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">「普通攻击」</span>造成的伤害+1。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_4312375945658558233.png",
                "id": "talent40121",
                "key": "清净之园囿",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/ad5eb2ee48365d340272b333689f3ebb_7755968433508292933.png",
                "title": "清净之园囿"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着水元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">蒸发</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">感电</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">草元素</span>】<span style=\"color: white\">绽放</span>：本伤害+1，生成使下次火元素或雷元素伤害+2的[<span style=\"color: white\">草原核</span>]</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/04/11/88072335/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_5553828223895712179.png",
                "id": "talent32412",
                "key": "水元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "水元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">泷廻鉴花</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p>所附属角色<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">普通攻击</span>造成的伤害+1，造成的<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>变为<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素伤害</span>。<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数：3</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/06/22/59155606/3b5977f18d39185ac0bc802fa291fb5f_8414105470975137729.png",
